Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:38.71,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(302,385)\fad(50,50)}校  对     万年妖受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:47.20,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要成为不管出什么事都不认输的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:47.20,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(285,245)\fad(50,50)}时  间     AKILA22
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:47.20,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(285,285)\fad(50,50)}后  期     Wesley
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:57.55,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然如此还是一定有弱小的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:00.96,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就保护他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:04.40,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这才能表现我们的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:11.28,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}从今天起我最勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:14.95,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.48,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强者出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:24.35,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}从今天起我最酷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:30.49,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}崭新的最强的NO.1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:32.35,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:40.44,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}的确从今天起 我就是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:13.97,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夢ならあるはずだ　あなたにも僕にでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:13.97,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每个人都有梦想 你我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:22.25,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}見つかりにくいだけだ忙しすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:22.25,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但因为太忙而很难被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:34.54,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ミエナイチカラで　だれもが強く繋がっている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:34.54,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谁都被看不到的力量强力的连接着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:39.67,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何も大したことじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:39.67,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:44.39,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そばにいても離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:44.39,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无论是否在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:49.20,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}昨日　今日　明日と
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:49.20,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}昨天 今天 明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:22:02.11,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔のあなたはいつでも　この胸にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:22:02.11,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的笑容永远深印在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:06.77,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You've got to be strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:09.26,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's never too late
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:13.24,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I never say die
